Russia’s Putin Says Nations’ Emissions Obligations Should Be Equalized

-- B y   I l y a   K h r e n n i k o v
-- 
2011-07-15T08:07:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-15/russia-s-putin-says-nations-emissions-obligations-should-be-equalized.html
Russian Prime Minister Vladimir said
countries’ obligations to reduce emissions under the  Kyoto
accord  should be equalized instead of allowing  developing
countries  to pollute more without paying fines. He spoke today
in Magnitogorsk in the  Ural Mountains .  To contact the reporter on this story:
